subSection.paragraph:
This work lists new names and misspellings published between 2020 and 2023 in the scale insects ( Hemiptera : Sternorrhyncha: Coccomorpha). For names at the genus level, this is the second supplement, following the comprehensive list by Williams & Denno (2014) and the first supplement of names published between 2014 and 2019 ( Williams & Denno 2020 ). Each genus name is attributed to a scale insect family accepted by most scale insect workers, as listed in ScaleNet online (
García Morales et al. 2022
). The short list of family-group names provided is a fourth supplement, following the third supplement of names published between 2013 and 2019 (Williams 2020). Each new family-group name is preceded by its nominal genus. Each new name is assigned to one of two informal groups, the archaeococcoids or the neococcoids, as proposed by Gullan & Cook (2007) .
